				<end-line
					>
				</end-line>
			</verse>
			<end-paragraph
				>
			</end-paragraph>
			<end-block-indent
				>
			</end-block-indent>
			<marker class="begin-verse" mid="v23052003">
			</marker>
			<begin-paragraph
				>
			</begin-paragraph>
			<verse num="3">
				For thus says the 
				<span class="divine-name">
					Lord
				</span>
				: 
				<crossref let="i" cid="c23052003.1">
				</crossref>
				<q class="begin-double" qid="" from="" to="">
				</q>
				You were sold for nothing, and 
				<crossref let="j" cid="c23052003.2">
				</crossref>
				you shall be redeemed without money.
				<q class="end-double" qid="" from="" to="">
				</q>
			</verse>
			<marker class="begin-verse" mid="v23052004">
			</marker>
			<verse num="4">
				For thus says the Lord 
				<span class="divine-name">
					God
				</span>
				: 
				<crossref let="k" cid="c23052004.1">
				</crossref>
				<q class="begin-double" qid="" from="" to="">
				</q>
				My people went down at the first into Egypt to sojourn there, and the Assyrian oppressed them for nothing.
			</verse>
			<marker class="begin-verse" mid="v23052005">
			</marker>
			<verse num="5">
				Now therefore what have I here,
				<q class="end-double" qid="" from="" to="">
				</q>
				 declares the 
				<span class="divine-name">
					Lord
				</span>
				, 
				<q class="begin-double" qid="" from="" to="">
				</q>
				seeing that my people are taken away for nothing? Their rulers wail,
				<q class="end-double" qid="" from="" to="">
				</q>
				 declares the 
				<span class="divine-name">
					Lord
				</span>
				, 
				<q class="begin-double" qid="" from="" to="">
				</q>
				and 
				<crossref let="l" cid="c23052005.1">
				</crossref>
				continually all the day my name is despised.
			</verse>
			<marker class="begin-verse" mid="v23052006">
			</marker>
			<verse num="6">
				Therefore my people shall know my name. 
				<crossref let="m" cid="c23052006.1">
				</crossref>
				Therefore in that day they shall know that it is I who speak; here am I.
				<q class="end-double" qid="" from="" to="">
				</q>
			</verse>
			<end-paragraph
				>
			</end-paragraph>
			<marker class="begin-verse" mid="v23052007">
			</marker>
			<begin-block-indent
				>
			</begin-block-indent>
			<begin-paragraph class="line-group">
			</begin-paragraph>
			<verse num="7">
				<begin-line
					>
				</begin-line>
				<crossref let="n" cid="c23052007.1">
				</crossref>
				How beautiful upon the mountains
				<end-line class="br">
				</end-line>
				<begin-line class="indent">
				</begin-line>
				are the feet of him who brings good news,
				<end-line class="br">
				</end-line>
				<begin-line
					>
				</begin-line>
				who publishes peace, 
				<crossref let="o" cid="c23052007.2">
				</crossref>
				who brings good news of happiness,
				<end-line class="br">
				</end-line>
				<begin-line class="indent">
				</begin-line>
				who publishes salvation,
				<end-line class="br">
				</end-line>
				<begin-line class="indent">
				</begin-line>
				who says to Zion, 
				<q class="begin-double" qid="" from="" to="">
				</q>
				Your God reigns.
				<q class="end-double" qid="" from="" to="">
				</q>
				<end-line class="br">
				</end-line>
			</verse>
			<marker class="begin-verse" mid="v23052008">
			</marker>
			<verse num="8">
				<begin-line
					>
				</begin-line>
				The voice of 
				<crossref let="p" cid="c23052008.1">
				</crossref>
				your watchmenùthey lift up their voice;
				<end-line class="br">
				</end-line>
				<begin-line class="indent">
				</begin-line>
				together they sing for joy;
				<end-line class="br">
				</end-line>
				<begin-line
					>
				</begin-line>
				<crossref let="q" cid="c23052008.2">
				</crossref>
				for eye to eye they see
				<end-line class="br">
				</end-line>
				<begin-line class="indent">
				</begin-line>
				the return of the 
				<span class="divine-name">
					Lord
				</span>
				 to Zion.
				<end-line class="br">
				</end-line>
			</verse>
			<marker class="begin-verse" mid="v23052009">
			</marker>
			<verse num="9">
				<begin-line
					>
				</begin-line>
				<crossref let="r" cid="c23052009.1">
				</crossref>
				Break forth together into singing,
				<end-line class="br">
				</end-line>
				<begin-line class="indent">
				</begin-line>
				<crossref let="s" cid="c23052009.2">
				</crossref>
				you waste places of Jerusalem,
				<end-line class="br">
				</end-line>
				<begin-line
					>
				</begin-line>
